
Chiron
======

Chiron is a system of CommonJS modules that introduce:

 * a type system
 * base types
 * general-purpose functions
 * events
 * optioned objects
 * caches and memos

Versions 0.2 and beyond are being developed here on Github.  The 0.1 
development train is in Subversion at Google Code [2].  

Node
----

    $ npm install chiron

Narwhal
-------

    $ tusk install chiron


